Yandex Text-to-Image-1B dataset
--------------------------------
Source: https://research.yandex.com/datasets/text-to-image-dataset-for-billion-scale-similarity-search
License: Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC BY 4.0)
         https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

This repository does not redistribute the dataset itself -- README.md points
users to big-ann-benchmarks to download it directly. The contents of
results/ and docs/ are derived benchmark statistics (recall, QPS, latency,
build time, index size) computed by running SereneDB/Qdrant/Elasticsearch
queries against indexes built from this dataset; no changes were made to the
dataset itself.

big-ann-benchmarks
------------------
Source: https://github.com/harsha-simhadri/big-ann-benchmarks
License: MIT License, Copyright (c) 2021 Martin Aumüller

